                    <b>Carrera - GO!!! - Lap Record!</b><br><br>The Carrera GO!!! Lap Record set guarantees you''re on the right track for motor racing passion with two slotcars to set a whole load of new track records. The spectators won''t be able to look away for even a second, lap after lap, whether you''re in the Red Bull Racing RB9 or the Ferrari F138. A loop, a fly-over, a junction and a high-speed straight are all packed into this 6.3-metre circuit to provide the biggest adrenaline kick a thoroughbred racedriver''s heart could possibly desire. Two high-performance cars are ready to roll and two very special drivers are raring to go. The GO!!! Lap Record! set offers great detailed cars, an authentic racing atmosphere, thrilling duels - and lots and lots of fun! Decide which car''s the one for you - and off you go! With lots of practice and ambition, your lap times will get better and better - and soon you''ll be setting new lap records!<br><br><b>Contents:</b><br><br><b>Cars:</b><ul><li>F138 "F.Alonso, No.3" (64010)</li><li>Racing RB9 "S.Vettel, No.1" (64009)</li></ul><b>Parts:</b><ul><li>Connecting Section</li><li>Instruction sheet</li><li>4x Double sliding contact</li><li>4x Fly Over 60°</li><li>5x Straight</li><li>2x Straight 114mm</li><li>2x Mechanical speed controller</li><li>Junction</li><li>2x Guide keels</li><li>6x Guardrail</li><li>24x Guardrail support</li><li>8x Looping set</li><li>Lapcounter analog</li><li>16x One touch clip</li><li>12x socket</li><li>Transformer</li></ul>
